{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_MM09_ED2_050.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x26,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0xffffffff,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "An ark to protect seeds...created in<CR>ancient times and mistakenly activated,<CR>had to be destroyed to rescue Nio."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0xffffffff,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "But, how right was it to defeat \"him\"? That question remained in Ayesha's heart, forcing her to make a decision."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0xffffffff,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "\"Let's look for the answer...!\""
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0xffffffff,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "To make amends? Or prove she did the<CR>right thing? Ayesha decides to take one<CR>more trip to the heights of alchemy..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "You're here. Hmm, your expression has improved."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Yes, I've made all the preparations for the journey."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "How prudent.<CR>...Is what I'd like to say, but..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Pursuing the truth will be a long journey."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "To part from the land you were born in must be accompanied by unbearable attachments."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Even if you are able to return to this land, you may be quite advanced in age by that time."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Knowing that, will you have no change of heart?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "...No. I've already decided."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "I need to find the answer about what I did in this land."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "In order to do so, I want to master the path of alchemy as much as I can."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Hmm, is that even possible? You would, at the very least, have to surpass me."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "If it's to discover the truth,<CR>I'm fully prepared to do that."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "If that is your decision, I won't allow you to go back on it, understand?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Yes."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "All right. Then I shall ask nothing more from you. However..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "It's none of my concern, but has your sister given her consent?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "I'm not sure if she agrees or not,<CR>but she said she'll be waiting."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "As long as we're both alive, we can see each other whenever we want... Even if we're apart...we'll be okay!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Jeez, you're so stubborn!<CR>Of course I'm not okay with this!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "N-Nio!?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "I'm gonna go with you! Even if you say I can't, I won't back down!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "So...take me with you..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Nio, you're always causing trouble...<CR>Mr. Keith...!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Will you return?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "No. I won't take back what I said. But, is it possible...to take her with me?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1d,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "It'll be a hard journey. The burden will be too much for your sister to bear."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x14,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1e,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "We'll be fine! If we're together!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1f,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "We'll be fine! If we're together!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x20,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Hmm... Hmhm, I guess you two are strong. Or perhaps just optimistic..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x21,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "I guess I should follow your example, as well."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x22,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Master, it is almost time for the stars to align."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x23,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Oh, then I shall open the door."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x24,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "All right. As your teacher, I shall pass down everything to you."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x25,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Sounds good! Now...let's go!"
        }
    ]
}